snippet.title: Best VGM 490 - Deep Labyrinth - A Brazing Breeze
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 81 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vp6NjZ0cGiI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Deep Labyrinth
A Brazing Breeze
